Cypriot Syllabary 	11th–4th centuries BCE
Cypriote Syllabary 
Cypriotic Syllabary was used ~900-300BC and developed from Cypro-Minoan, 
which in turn was influenced by Linear-A or a common ancestor BEFORE and in parallel to Linear-B.

